und. They didn=E2=80=99t get cashed out, and their stock still trades publi=
cly. Or, rather, they <em>did=C2=A0</em>get cashed out =E2=80=94=C2=A0QXO/S=
ilverSun will pay the pre-deal SilverSun shareholders a dividend of $17.4 m=
illion, which is roughly equal to SilverSun=E2=80=99s entire market capital=
ization as of last November<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-2"=
