l trades on the Nasdaq.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Which creates a ver=
y weird dynamic. QXO is not=C2=A0<em>really=C2=A0</em>a public company. It =
is an=C2=A0investment vehicle for Brad Jacobs to acquire=C2=A0some companie=
