rs. The acquisitions=C2=A0haven=E2=80=99t happened yet, and=C2=A0most of th=
at $4.5 billion of investor money hasn=E2=80=99t come in yet. Jacobs and hi=
s investors did put in $1 billion for their stock already, but that stock i=
