<div id=3D"footnote-1" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[1] The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/35746803.259295/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9l=
